implementation-defined-item.name: sequenceNormalization
implementation-defined-item.value: Sequences are returned as Java Iterators over an X-Hive specific mapping of the XQuery type system to a Java object hierarchy. Serialization is left to the user, though a default toString() method is provided and returned XML nodes implement org.w3c.dom.Node, so they can be used with DOM serializers.
